== Introduction ==
The Georgia Gala is a Live Action Role-Playing event for players of Vampire: The Masquerade Mind's Eye Theatre. The Georgia Gala is being run by the Stolen Hours chronicle, a member in good standing with One World by Night.

The Georgia Gala will be held February 24th through 25th of 2012 in Atlanta, Georgia at the Atlanta Marriot Suites Midtown.

If you're interesting in finding out more contact ST_STAFF_EMAIL

[kindred_prom.jpg]


