=== Book a room at the Atlanta Marriot Suites Midtown ===
This year we’re hosting the event at the Marriott Suites Midtown, in the heart of Midtown Atlanta.  We have a block of rooms reserved at a rate of $129 a night, for either a King Suite or Double Double Suite.  The suites have sofa beds and can sleep 5. Mention the group “One World by Night” to get the group rate. 

[Atlanta Marriot Suites Midtown http://www.marriott.com/hotels/travel/atlms?groupCode=ownowna&app=resvlink&fromDate=2/24/12&toDate=2/26/12] [[""http://www.marriott.com/Images/Brands/MHR/Logos/MHR_logowhitefield_120x60"".gif] http://www.marriott.com/hotels/travel/atlms?groupCode=ownowna&app=resvlink&fromDate=2/24/12&toDate=2/26/12]


