=== Things to do in Atlanta ===

The hotel is convenient to many attractions in Atlanta.  [The High Museum of Art http://www.high.org] is within walking distance, and the [Atlanta Botanical Gardens http://www.atlantabotanicalgarden.org/] are also fairly close.  Other attractions include the [Georgia Aquarium http://www.georgiaaquarium.org/], [The World of Coke http://www.worldofcoca-cola.com/], and the [CNN Center http://www.cnn.com/tour/].  The hotel website has a good list of attractions and their websites: [http://www.marriott.com/hotels/local-things-to-do/atlms-atlanta-marriott-suites-midtown/ http://www.marriott.com/hotels/local-things-to-do/atlms-atlanta-marriott-suites-midtown/]


